Sample Entry: Constant value of 'TH' for all entries
Label: Transaction History ID
Description: Record identifier for transaction history records. Constant 'TH' indicates Transaction History.

Sample Entry: Text/Mixed data. 530 unique values. Samples: CGRIA3200      , CGRVA4335      , SPR3281        , SPS3405        , SPR4101
Label: Product Code
Description: Product code involved in the transaction. 530 unique products.

Sample Entry: Discrete values: 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6
Label: Sequence Number
Description: Transaction sequence number for multiple transactions on same order/item.

Sample Entry: Discrete values: # , B , C , DP, DS, IG, IW, IZ, T+, T-
Label: Transaction Type
Description: Type of transaction code (# for adjustment, B for BOM, C for cycle count, DP/DS for production, IG for goods in, IW for warehouse, IZ for inventory zero, T+/T- for transfers).

Sample Entry: Constant value of '20210125' for all entries
Label: Transaction Date
Description: Date when transaction occurred. Value 20210125 (January 25 2021).

Sample Entry: Lots of 0's (88.9%), Range from -1292.0 to 998.0, Contains decimal values
Label: Transaction Quantity
Description: Quantity of items in the transaction. Mostly zeros with range from -1292 to 998.

Sample Entry: Discrete values:   , C4, C5, CZ, GA, MB, QC
Label: Warehouse
Description: Warehouse code for the transaction. Warehouses: C4, C5, CZ, GA, MB, QC.

Sample Entry: Discrete values:       , C4    , C5    , CZ    , GA    , QC
Label: Location Code
Description: Specific location within warehouse for the transaction.

Label: Unit Price
Description: Unit price or cost of item at time of transaction. Range from 0 to 12296.8.

Sample Entry: Lots of 0's (92.3%), Range from 0 to 446011
Label: Reference Number
Description: Reference number for the transaction (e.g., Order #, PO #, Invoice #). Mostly zeros.

Sample Entry: Lots of 0's (95.7%), Range from -23978.12 to 2079.95, Contains decimal values
Label: Transaction Value
Description: Total monetary value of the transaction. Mostly zeros with range -23978 to 2079.

Label: Settlement Date
Description: Date of settlement or shipping. Various dates in January 2021.

Label: Secondary Reference
Description: Additional reference number or manufacturing order number.

Sample Entry: Text/Mixed data. 16 unique values. Samples: T L F PC ALL 02, P L F PC ALL 02, P L F PC ALL 03, P L F PC ALL 04, P L F PC ALL 02 is used for hundreds of values.
Label: Comment
Description: Comment or description code for the transaction (e.g., 'P L F PC ALL 02' appears frequently).

Sample Entry: Discrete values: CA, EL, GR, IO, IR, IS, ME, PG, PS, PU, PZ, TF, TR, TS
Label: Transaction Class
Description: Classification code for transaction type (CA, EL, GR, IO, IR, IS, ME, PG, PS, PU, PZ, TF, TR, TS).

Sample Entry: Discrete values: 1, BA, P1, P8, PD, PL, PO, RA, S1, S2, S3, S4, SR, TC
Label: Reason Code
Description: Reason or source code for the transaction (1, BA, P1, P8, PD, PL, PO, RA, S1-S4, SR, TC).

Sample Entry: Discrete values: Primarily 0, 1410, 1653
Label: Vendor ID
Description: Vendor or supplier identifier. Mostly 0 with some values 1410, 1653.

Sample Entry: Discrete values:  Primary blank values, Y
Label: Status
Description: Transaction status indicator. Mostly blank with some 'Y' values.

Sample Entry: Lots of 0's (88.9%), Range from 0.0 to 1051.81, Contains decimal values
Label: Standard Cost
Description: Standard cost of the item. Mostly zeros with range 0 to 1051.81.

Label: Workstation ID
Description: Workstation or terminal identifier where transaction was entered.

Sample Entry: Discrete values: K2B       , LUPABE    , MAGGDY01  , MAGZAM01  , MOJMA     , OGOLNY01  , OSIKAJU   , WCISLOJO
Label: User ID
Description: User identifier who performed the transaction.

Sample Entry: Range from 75450 to 101825
Label: Transaction Time
Description: Time when transaction occurred (HHMMSS format). Range 075450 to 101825.

Sample Entry: Discrete values:  EUR, PLN, USD, GBP
Label: Currency
Description: Currency code for transaction values (EUR, PLN, USD, GBP).

Label: Exchange Rate
Description: Exchange rate used for currency conversion. Values include 1.0, 4.4493, 4.5407.

Sample Entry: Lots of 0's (94.9%), Range from 0.0 to 94.08, Contains decimal values
Label: Order Quantity
Description: Original order quantity or reference quantity. Mostly zeros.

Label: GL Rate
Description: General Ledger rate or accounting factor for financial posting.
Keywords: rate; gl; general ledger; accounting; financial

Label: Order Number
Description: Order number associated with the transaction.

Sample Entry: Constant value of '0' for all entries
Label: Operation Number
Description: Operation number within the manufacturing order.

Sample Entry: Lots of 0's (96.9%), Range from 0 to 4708
Label: Work Center
Description: Work center code where the operation was performed.
Keywords: work center; location; manufacturing; station; facility

Sample Entry: Constant value of '0' for all entries
Label: Parent Shortage
Description: Flag indicating if there is a shortage for the parent item.

Label: Line Number
Description: Line number of the order or transaction.

Sample Entry: Discrete values:   , BX, KG, SZ, TH, PL, ZG, EA, TN, BX, FT (some form of Unit of Measure Table)
Label: Transaction UOM
Description: Unit of measure used for the transaction quantity.

Sample Entry: Lots of 0's (94.2%), Range from -1292.0 to 998.0, Contains decimal values
Label: Quantity in UOM
Description: Quantity expressed in the transaction unit of measure.

Sample Entry: Lots of 0's (92.1%), Range from 0.0 to 1039.97938, Contains decimal values
Label: Actual Cost
Description: Actual cost of the item for this transaction.

Sample Entry: Discrete values: 0, 8484
Label: Run Number
Description: Run number for production or processing.

Sample Entry: Discrete values: 0, 1, 2, 3, 4
Label: Run Sequence
Description: Sequence number within the run.

Sample Entry: Constant value of '0' for all entries
Label: Next Item Index
Description: Index or pointer to the next item record.

Label: Comment
Description: Additional comments or codes associated with the transaction.

Sample Entry: Constant value of '0' for all entries
Label: Foreign Amount
Description: Transaction amount in foreign currency.

Sample Entry: Discrete values:  , G
Label: Remarks Flag
Description: Flag indicating if remarks are present.

Sample Entry: Constant value of '0' for all entries
Label: Start Time
Description: Start time of the transaction or operation.

Sample Entry: Values such as: WCISLOJO, DBAK, BIJALDMA, WALCZYWI, SZLAPAAG, CHWASTEL
Label: Created By
Description: User ID of the person who created the record.
Keywords: created by; user; id; author; origin

Sample Entry: Discrete values: 0, 20210125
Label: Creation Date
Description: Date when the record was created.

Sample Entry: Discrete values: 0, 101621
Label: Creation Time
Description: Time when the record was created.

Sample Entry: Constant value of '0' for all entries
Label: Last Date
Description: Date of the last update to the record.

Sample Entry: Constant value of '0' for all entries
Label: Last Time
Description: Time of the last update to the record.

Sample Entry: Constant value of '0' for all entries
Label: Unit Price Indicator
Description: Indicator for how unit price is applied.

Sample Entry: Constant value of '0' for all entries
Label: Consignment Flag
Description: Flag indicating if the item is consignment inventory.

Sample Entry: Discrete values: 0, 1
Label: Exchange Rate Type 2
Description: Secondary exchange rate type.

Sample Entry: Constant value of '1' for all entries
Label: GL Rate Type 2
Description: Secondary General Ledger rate type.

Sample Entry: Discrete values:  , 7, 8
Label: Comment Type B
Description: Type code for the second comment field.
